page.title: 07A Day in the life
page.content: Sharon (11) Wed 16 May Got up at{08.00}had breakfast of coffee and toast then fed my rabbit.Set off for school {08.30.}Reached school chatted to Zoe my friend until 09.00.Started maths (sets).Playtime 10.30 had playpiece of Milky Way. Came in and went to music {11.46}came out 12.26.Went to packed lunches had Branston Pickle and cheese sandwiches,crisps,apple and Kio-ra drink.Went outside chatted until{13.30 came in and did S.R.A.Went out chatted came in and did history.Went to sewing {15.00}until 15.30.Came home.Went to library.Had tea 16.40.Let rabbit out.Went to look for sister 17.30 came back 18.00.Had supper of coffee and biscuits.Watched T.V until 21.27.Went to bed.
